<headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 02 at 5:18AM EDT  by NWS NorthernIndiana</headline>
<description>...Patchy Dense Fog Early This Morning...
Patchy dense shallow ground fog will result in locally reduced
visibilities. If travelling, be alert for sudden reductions in
visibility. If dense fog is encountered, use your low beams,
reduce speed, and increase following distance. Fog should diminish
shortly after sunrise.</description>
